  "type": "<one of: lesson-plan | quiz-generator | visual-aid-designer | worksheet-wizard | virtual-field-trip | teacher-training | rubric-generator | exam-paper | video-storyteller | instantAnswer | unknown>",
  "topic": "<extracted topic or null>",
  "gradeLevel": "<Class N or null>",
  "subject": "<subject or null>",
  "language": "<ISO code or null>"
}
```

Respond ONLY with the JSON object — no surrounding prose, no markdown fences.
